<img class="post_image aligncenter" src="http://www.howtovanish.com/images/watch-getting-started.jpg" width="520" height="94" alt="watch getting started" />
					<h1>Why We Started HowToVanish And Who We Are</h1>
				</div>
				<div class="format_text">
            <a href="http://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" 
